==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Peek
<hw>Peek</hw> <pr>(p⟦emac⟧k)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>piken</ets>: cf. F. <ets>piquer</ets> to pierce, prick, E.
<ets>pique</ets>. Cf. <er>Peak</er>.]</ety> <def>To look
surreptitiously, or with the eyes half closed, or through a crevice; to
peep.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Peekaboo</ent>⟦br⟧
